\v 25 Not kab…®, nak ji da gen pas…®l…® k…®nda tosok uŇčun dakon mib…®l…® nandaba p…®sosak do nand…®sat. YaŇč kaŇč d…®si do d…®ma nandaba w…®g…®sak. Gen pas…®l…® uŇčun yaŇč: Israel am…®n d…®war…® PiŇčkop da but yomani sopgut uŇčun yaŇč eg…® w…®gakwa Am…®n ŇäwakŇčwar…® Kab…® niaŇč da iy…®kon apni do t…®lak y…®pgut uŇčun da ar…®pmon iy…®kon apdaŇč.
\v 26 \x - \xo 11:26 \xt Ais 59.20-21\x*Ae don PiŇčkop da Israel am…®n morap k…®si yokwikon baŇč t…®m…®td…®sak. UŇčun do PiŇčkop gen papia da yaŇč yosok:
